OL,3,CMeet Europe's oldest triathlete
OL,4,Crepresenting Wales and Team GB
OL,6,FAt 72, Wayne Richards isn't letting
OL,7,Fthe fact he's a pensioner get in the
OL,8,Fway of chasing personal bests and
OL,9,Fmedals.
OL,11,F"Age is just a number, isn't it?" the
OL,12,FMumbles ironman says with a grin.
OL,14,FWayne is Europe's oldest triathlete
OL,15,Fwho recently returned from the
OL,16,FEuropean Championships last week where
OL,17,Fhe represented Team GB.
