OL,3,CMeet Europe's oldest triathlete
OL,4,Crepresenting Wales and Team GB
OL,6,FWhat makes Wayne's feat even more
OL,7,Fremarkable is that he only took up
OL,8,Ftraining for triathlons seven years
OL,9,Fago, at the age of 65, after a chance
OL,10,Fencounter with athletes taking part in
OL,11,Fthe Swansea Sprint Triathlon.
OL,13,FFrom that moment he says he was
OL,14,F"hooked" and now he's about to
OL,15,Frepresent Wales at the UK
OL,16,FChampionships later this month.
OL,18,F"It's quite an honour really, I never
OL,19,Fthought I'd be doing this at my age!",
OL,20,Fhe told ITV Wales News.
