OL,3,CMeet Europe's oldest triathlete
OL,4,Crepresenting Wales and Team GB
OL,6,FWayne added: "I enjoy it, there is a
OL,7,Fpurpose to my exercise at the moment.
OL,8,FBefore I was doing triathlons there
OL,9,Fwasn't much purpose for going to the
OL,10,Fgym, I used to go just to keep fit.
OL,11,FNow the fitness comes naturally, I've
OL,12,Fnever been so fit."
OL,14,FWayne always loved competing and began
OL,15,Fswimming at the outdoor pool in
OL,16,FYstalyfera when he was a child.
