OL,3,CMeet Europe's oldest triathlete
OL,4,Crepresenting Wales and Team GB
OL,6,FHis six-day-a-week training regime
OL,7,Fincludes running across Gower,
OL,8,Fswimming in Langland Bay, and cycling
OL,9,Ffrom Mumbles to Neath and over the
OL,10,Fmountains of the Dulais Valley.
OL,12,FHe said: "Today (Monday) is my day off
OL,13,Fbut tomorrow I have to do a swim and a
OL,14,Frun, well I don't have to do it, I
OL,15,Fchoose to do it!
OL,17,F"The following day I have to ride my
OL,18,Fbike and so on for the rest of the
OL,19,Fweek until next Monday when I finally
OL,20,Fget a day off again."
