OL,3,CMeet Europe's oldest triathlete
OL,4,Crepresenting Wales and Team GB
OL,6,FMost competitive athletes contemplate
OL,7,Fretirement in their mid to late 30s -
OL,8,Fnot Wayne though, he's got his focus
OL,9,Fset on the next European Championships
OL,10,Fin Istanbul, with no plans to hang up
OL,11,Fhis Team GB vest just yet.
OL,13,FHe added: "My body will tell me when I
OL,14,Fhave to stop and at the moment it's
OL,15,Fnot telling me to stop, so I'll carry
OL,16,Fon."
